 → development/databases/Oracle/installed/dynamic-performance-views/instance/[v$instance]

 v$instance_recovery can be used to determine the → http://www.adp-gmbh.ch/ora/concepts/redo_log.html#optimal_size[optimal size] for → → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/redo-log-files[log files].

 → development/databases/Oracle/installed/dynamic-performance-views/iostat/file/[v$iostat_file]

