 v$pwfile_users: Lists all users who have been granted → http://www.adp-gmbh.ch/ora/admin/sysdba.html[sysdba] or → http://www.adp-gmbh.ch/ora/admin/system_privileges.html#sysoper[sysoper] privileges.
 See → http://www.adp-gmbh.ch/ora/admin/password_file.html#adding_user[adding users to the password file].

